  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.description': 'Everything you need a know about pip calculations',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q1.answer': 'A pip (Point en porcentage) is the peque√±asest price movimiento en forex. para most pares (EUR/USD, GBP/USD), a pip is the 4th decimal place: 0.0001. Example: EUR/USD movimientos desde 1.0850 a 1.0851 = 1 pip movimiento. Exception: JPY pares use 2 decimals, so a pip is 0.01. Example: USD/JPY 149.50 a 149.51 = 1 pip. Some brokers quote fractional pips (pipettes/points) as 5th decimal: 1.08501 - cada pipette is 1/10th de a pip.',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q1.question': '¬øQu√© es exactamente un \'pip\' y c√≥mo se mide?',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q2.answer': 'For crosses like EUR/GBP o AUD/NZD, pip value calculation requierens two conversi√≥ns a your account moneda. Formula: (0.0001 / current exchange rate) √ó lote size √ó counter moneda a account moneda rate. c√≥moever, our calculator handles this automatically. Example: EUR/GBP con USD account - calculator uses GBP/USD rate a convert GBP pip value a USD. Manual calculation complex, always use calculator para crosses a avoid errors.',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q2.question': 'c√≥mo do I Calcular pip value para pares where USD is not involved (cross pares)?',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q3.answer': 'Three main Raz√≥ns: 1) Spread cost - Calculator sc√≥mos gross P/L, but you pay bid/ask spread (T√≠picoly 1-3 pips sobre entry). Subtract spread desde beneficio. 2) Overnight swap/rollover - Holding positions overnight incurs interest charges o credits, not reflected en pip calculations. 3) Slippage - durante fast markets (news events), your exit Mayo be 2-5 pips worse than intended, especially sobre stop p√©rdidaes. Calculator assumes porfect execution en exact pip count. para accurate P/L, deduct spreads y factor en realistic slippage (5-10 pips para stops durante news).',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q3.question': 'Why does my actual beneficio/p√©rdida sometimes differ desde the calculator?',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q4.answer': 'est√°ndar lote = 100,000 units de base moneda. sobre EUR/USD: 1 lote = $10 por pip. Mini lote = 10,000 units (0.1 lote). EUR/USD: 0.1 lote = $1 por pip. Micro lote = 1,000 units (0.01 lote). EUR/USD: 0.01 lote = $0.10 por pip. Use est√°ndar lotees con large cuentas ($50K+), Mini lotees para cuentas $5K-$50K, y Micro lotees para learning o cuentas <$5K. cada step down reduces riesgo por 90%, making Micro lotees ideal para beginners a practice without riesgoing significant capital.',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q4.question': '¬øCu√°l es la diferencia entre lotes est√°ndar, mini y micro?',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q5.answer': 'Reverse calculation method: 1) Decide max riesgo en dollars (e.g., $100 = 2% de $5K account). 2) Measure stop p√©rdida distance en pips (e.g., 50 pips desde entry a stop). 3) funcionan backward: requierend lote size = riesgo ($100) / (pips (50) √ó pip value por lote). para EUR/USD: $100 / (50 √ó $10) = 0.2 lotees. Enter different lote sizes en calculator until P/L en your pip distance equals your dollar riesgo. This ensures consistent riesgo por trade regardless de stop p√©rdida width.',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q5.question': 'c√≥mo can I use this calculator a determine my position size?',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q6.answer': 'For USD-account pares where USD is the counter moneda (EUR/USD, GBP/USD, AUD/USD), pip value is fixed en $10 por est√°ndar lote throughout the trade. para pares where USD is the base (USD/JPY, USD/CHF) o cross pares (EUR/GBP), pip value fluctuates con exchange rate changes - but the difference is usually negligible (<5%) para short-term trades. Our calculator uses current rates. para accuracy sobre long-term positions (weeks/months), reCalcular pip value if exchange rates movimiento significantly (>10%).',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q6.question': 'Does pip value change durante the trade, o is it fixed?',
  'tools.pipCalculator.faq.q7.answer': 'Calculator sc√≥mos gross P/L before commission. If your broker charges commission (e.g., $3.50 por lote por side): 1) Calcular pip P/L normally. 2) Subtract commission: para 1 lote EUR/USD = $7 total ($3.50 open + $3.50 close). 3) Adjust para breakeven: con $7 commission sobre 1 lote ($10/pip), you need 0.7 pip movimiento just a break even. para 50 pip beneficio sc√≥mon en calculator, actual net = 50 pips √ó $10 - $7 = $493. Consider commission-free brokers (spread-only) para peque√±aser cuentas o frequent trading a avoid commission eating into beneficios.',
